{"tid":218970,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"慢遊紐約 求建議","createTime":"2017-04-27T01:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T02:47:47.000Z","uid":27280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3ee0d8995f6c62c371d9656ddbc37b91d61e84","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲有無咩隠世紐約好去處<br />\n不論食，玩，睇<br />\n<br />\n另外 去嗰邊有咩建議/注意事項<br />\n例如交通 節日 旅遊指南 機場過關等<br />\n<br />\n週邊有咩地方值得去 (Phily? DC? Boston? )<br />\n求教<br />\n<br />\n利申：想六月尾慢遊 一個月 budget 8-10k 唔使book住宿 3餐可隨時返去食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5fb66dbb68f3831322e7032e6cbfb0fd2d882","tid":218970,"uid":80397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"一個月8-10k?<br />\n當你一個人住Manhattan<br />\n兩個禮拜酒店錢都唔夠比喎"},{"pid":"a38827e0c7e023fec13989d3b6a877b403e8ae88","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月8-10k?<br />\n當你一個人住Manhattan<br />\n兩個禮拜酒店錢都唔夠比喎</blockquote><br />\n唔使比住宿，有安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dae2e3793d99e5261d9926bf69702b49dea33b6","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f995c9910561c69e3dbb677bc05188472c1503ee","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"cebbbe849eb73e7bf11796205bba12d279e59ee6","tid":218970,"uid":113909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"留一個月 到步立即買左monthly metro card 先喇 搭車都幾貴下"},{"pid":"fa4dc174cd3a6433df697c33b6e3e553a422e5ad","tid":218970,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"上年都係6,7月左右同屋企人去咗NYC 7日<br />\n主要join local tour <br />\n只有一日自己出去行下<br />\nNYC好多museum<br />\nCentral park 裡面都有好幾個<br />\n睇完可以去Cental park hea下<br />\n跟住再慢慢行落去Time square 睇下嘢<br />\n另外一日可坐船睇下自由神像 <br />\n但好多強國大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你會唔會揸車？<br />\n如果揸車就可以落DC + Philly <br />\nDC 都值得去<br />\n始終係首都 （果到空氣超好）<br />\n唔揸就join local tour <br />\n但預咗有好多強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋係睇完影個相就走<br />\n如果你想入去白宮睇<br />\n好似要至少唔知幾個月前上網book<br />\n你可以睇下台灣 d blog<br />\n佢地好多自由行的行程都值得參考下<br />\n不過一個月stay East coast 會有d悶<br />\n除非有親戚朋友喺當地<br />\n反而west coast 多嘢玩好多"},{"pid":"101639073f1f1a505cef937912371231b77b9b79","tid":218970,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"moma. 同其他博物館慢慢行<br />\n有成1 個月 可以一日睇1個博物館<br />\ndc都可以去 有白宮 又有勁大博物館<br />\n都去左東岸當然要去下<br />\nny唐人街有巴士落dc 好平。<br />\n可以慢遊dc 2-3日"},{"pid":"d941deae5f5aa8c424fc79b8eebdb6d0759d5033","tid":218970,"uid":72927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"去下Brooklyn bridge影相 華爾街睇金牛 Times Square/Central Park9行影相 食下出名野食shake shack/buffalo wings"},{"pid":"9fc6974d56aa8fe8b806838d381264d4d189c10e","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"謝各位 ching"},{"pid":"744f5fff4e916c42440f808fb435904b4f85e545","tid":218970,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"385ebf5491a6d4ec067db51e5281a32d8d500ee1","tid":218970,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月8-10k?<br />\n當你一個人住Manhattan<br />\n兩個禮拜酒店錢都唔夠比喎</blockquote><br />\n我終於知道咩叫盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fbf68693237cd6c3c021507c5428d6b29592ce","tid":218970,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:28:54.000Z","msg":"<bl